{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1013924, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "上古八大姓，哪个和父系有关？\n姬、姜、姒、嬴、妘、妫、姚、姞", "timestamp": 1611917155, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013928, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不过是从母系社会抢过来的东西", "timestamp": 1611917186, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013931, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "原Alice来了，我是说现代汉语中的“姓”的这个概念，不是说这个字", "timestamp": 1611917189, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013934, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实是从母系社会抢来的东西啊，我没否认，，", "timestamp": 1611917207, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但这区别大概近似于古希腊民主和现代民主一样吧", "timestamp": 1611917229, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013953, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我认为姓在某方面对男性进行了约束。这个孩子是我生的，所以母亲自然疼爱孩子；这个孩子跟我姓相同，所以也约束了父亲去履行对孩子的责任", "timestamp": 1611917317, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013954, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 呸", "timestamp": 1611917327, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013957, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 女权就是要废除主流父系传承啊，母系父系各表一枝，原dz显然是问现代平等意义上凭啥要姓父姓，没错就是要反对父权，你却觉得理所当然", "timestamp": 1611917365, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1013969, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202141, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "t